# Reviews

Review notes, feedback, assessments, and quality documents.

## What Goes Here

- Document and content reviews
- Process and project retrospectives
- Quality assessments
- Security and compliance findings
- Code review feedback when the campaign includes software

## Structure

```
reviews/
├── <review>/          # Active reviews at root
├── templates/         # Review templates
└── dungeon/           # Archived reviews
    ├── completed/
    ├── archived/
    └── someday/
```

## Guidelines

- Link reviews to the work or artifact being assessed
- Track decisions and follow-up actions
- Use `camp dungeon crawl` to triage completed reviews into dungeon
